{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019/04/04/tomatobeef/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c69ed781-87c9-5a6a-bbbf-f4446611ac47","html":"<p><del>我这是在干什么2.0</del></p>\n<p>中超需求为生抽/味精，也可以考虑不使用。</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<p>一个有趣的事实是，本系列的主角均是英国便利店（Tesco)可以买到的食材，大家可以脑补一个在便利店对着冰鲜柜台思考菜谱的笔者。</p>\n<p>以下材料为两人份（准确地说是一人两餐份，汪汪）</p>\n<p><strong>原料</strong>：</p>\n<p>牛腩 400g</p>\n<p>土豆 2个（350g)</p>\n<p>番茄 4个（~300g)</p>\n<p>生姜 半块（10-20g）</p>\n<p>大蒜 n瓣（40g)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/80bab/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92.11822660098522%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/627f4/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/efcb5/1.jpg 203w,\n/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/02e66/1.jpg 405w,\n/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/627f4/1.jpg 810w,\n/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/78959/1.jpg 1215w,\n/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/0047d/1.jpg 1620w,\n/static/61094bd926d6d6ffa66916d4e7050d59/80bab/1.jpg 3008w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>调料</strong>：</p>\n<p>盐 生抽 味精 胡椒碎 食用油 番茄酱</p>\n<p><strong>关于选料</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>这里的牛腩是Tesco的Diced Beef，自己买成块的切小丁也没差。以未速冻的新鲜肉为宜。</li>\n<li>嫌大蒜内皮难剥可以试试把头尾去掉，会自然地带下一部分皮。</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>流程</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>锅内加入适量开水，煮沸后加入牛腩炖煮3分钟左右，撇去浮沫。捞出牛腩，肉汤留下待用。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/21f5f/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.25123152709361%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/627f4/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/efcb5/2.jpg 203w,\n/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/02e66/2.jpg 405w,\n/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/627f4/2.jpg 810w,\n/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/78959/2.jpg 1215w,\n/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/0047d/2.jpg 1620w,\n/static/e5f6a04610019a841e1002ac9aaf1873/21f5f/2.jpg 3365w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>番茄切块，姜切片，蒜切碎末。土豆去皮后亦切块（可以切小一点，图中的过大了）</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/f543b/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.81773399014777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/627f4/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/efcb5/3.jpg 203w,\n/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/02e66/3.jpg 405w,\n/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/627f4/3.jpg 810w,\n/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/78959/3.jpg 1215w,\n/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/0047d/3.jpg 1620w,\n/static/1e363e51b42d50e167eeecbc8a941dda/f543b/3.jpg 3742w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>起锅入油，炒番茄至出汁，根据个人口味加入番茄酱。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/1fedd/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92.11822660098522%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/627f4/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/efcb5/4.jpg 203w,\n/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/02e66/4.jpg 405w,\n/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/627f4/4.jpg 810w,\n/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/78959/4.jpg 1215w,\n/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/0047d/4.jpg 1620w,\n/static/a59e8383d6be2600a85bc59ff5f2c398/1fedd/4.jpg 3112w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>放入土豆与牛腩，翻炒均匀后加入盐、味精、胡椒碎。加入少量生抽调色（喜欢原色的话也可以不加）</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/1c916/5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.36945812807883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/627f4/5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/efcb5/5.jpg 203w,\n/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/02e66/5.jpg 405w,\n/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/627f4/5.jpg 810w,\n/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/78959/5.jpg 1215w,\n/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/0047d/5.jpg 1620w,\n/static/329f9fdba0d35910e28d970b217e809c/1c916/5.jpg 3446w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>加入牛肉汤（控制量，以没过大部分食材为宜），加盖开中火炖煮40分钟左右。期间时不时用锅铲翻动食材，防止糊底。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/aa2fd/6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.8768472906404%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/627f4/6.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/efcb5/6.jpg 203w,\n/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/02e66/6.jpg 405w,\n/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/627f4/6.jpg 810w,\n/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/78959/6.jpg 1215w,\n/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/0047d/6.jpg 1620w,\n/static/2d72c4df03e7b1d4caeb347b17e6102a/aa2fd/6.jpg 3067w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>煮至汤汁成粘稠酱状，土豆可轻松用锅铲切开出锅。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/7ea51/7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.25123152709361%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/627f4/7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/efcb5/7.jpg 203w,\n/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/02e66/7.jpg 405w,\n/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/627f4/7.jpg 810w,\n/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/78959/7.jpg 1215w,\n/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/0047d/7.jpg 1620w,\n/static/b2545d8b116299c2b8a3c6ec39ff77ba/7ea51/7.jpg 3375w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>煮个米饭，开吃（似曾相识的结尾）</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 810px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/32ae66e17258b7694429641b5c26cd19/99661/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.47290640394088%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/32ae66e17258b7694429641b5c26cd19/d7542/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/32ae66e17258b7694429641b5c26cd19/2efce/8.png 203w,\n/static/32ae66e17258b7694429641b5c26cd19/1d180/8.png 405w,\n/static/32ae66e17258b7694429641b5c26cd19/d7542/8.png 810w,\n/static/32ae66e17258b7694429641b5c26cd19/99661/8.png 1098w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>注意事项</strong>：40分钟仅为约数，请自行控制炖煮时间。过程需要时不时翻动食材，否则后半段黏度过高的时候很容易糊底。</p>\n<p>下期可能做西餐……？</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"ZH家的饭 2 番茄土豆牛肉煲","date":"2019-04-04","categories":"杂学","message":null,"tags":["菜谱"]},"fields":{"encrypted":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/04/02/britain_diary1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"旅居随笔·伦敦篇"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/06/06/bannerofmaid/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"新时代的复古SPRG——《圣女战旗》"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"c69ed781-87c9-5a6a-bbbf-f4446611ac47","previousPostId":"f26d16ac-9ab4-5ffc-bd97-6e6abb9e5227","nextPostId":"da82d9ba-2f97-567e-b305-4defcd2c74f6"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1605745662","2212765230","2826202570","3000541721","3274528899","3390260504","3406122720","3823010829","689422991"]}